r_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"I can upload the `colors` in `Uint8Array`  with raw WebGL by following code:\n\n```\nvar colors = new Uint8Array(triangles * 3 * 4);\n\nfor (var i = 0, l = triangles * 3 * 4; i < l; i += 4) {\n\n  colors[i] = Math.random() * 255;\n  colors[i + 1] = Math.random() * 255;\n  colors[i + 2] = Math.random() * 255;\n  colors[i + 3] = Math.random() * 255;\n\n}\n...\nvar vertexColorBuffer = gl.createBuffer();\nvar vertexColorAttribute = gl.getAttribLocation(program, 'color');\ngl.enableVertexAttribArray(vertexColorAttribute);\ngl.bindBuffer(gl.ARRAY_BUFFER, vertexColorBuffer);\ngl.bufferData(gl.ARRAY_BUFFER, colors, gl.STATIC_DRAW);\ngl.bindBuffer(gl.ARRAY_BUFFER, vertexColorBuffer);\ngl.vertexAttribPointer(vertexColorAttribute, 4, gl.UNSIGNED_BYTE, true, 0, 0);\n\n```\n\nAs my understanding, the `setupVertexAttributes` (https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob\/three.js\/blob\/master\/src\/renderers\/WebGLRenderer.js#L994) only handles `_gl.FLOAT` type.\n","created_at":"2016-03-15T02:14:52.000Z","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/8358#issuecomment-196617542","id":196617542,"issue_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/8358","node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDE5NjYxNzU0Mg==","updated_at":"2016-03-15T02:14:52.000Z","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/comments\/196617542","user":{"following_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/huningxin\/following{\/other_user}","events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/huningxin\/events{\/privacy}","avatar_url":"https:\/\/avatars1.githubusercontent.com\/u\/1005673?v=4","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/huningxin","gists_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/huningxin\/gists{\/gist_id}","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/huningxin","subscriptions_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/huningxin\/subscriptions","node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEwMDU2NzM=","repos_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/huningxin\/repos","received_events_url":"